# Architecture standards

## Structured error responses
All API errors must return { error: { code, message } } format.

## Use TypeScript
Use TypeScript as part of the standard tech stack.

## Use React
Use React as part of the standard tech stack.

## Use MongoDB
Use MongoDB as part of the standard tech stack.

## Use Vitest
Use Vitest as part of the standard tech stack.

## Use Kubernetes
Use Kubernetes as part of the standard tech stack.
